{"tid":1343181,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［香城online中的模擬市民］開party有咩方法拯救狗公圍住既美女","createTime":"2019-07-21T18:24:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T05:50:00.000Z","uid":57018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3b495b30afad5155eba5d3fa025bd4d02f7f8527","tid":1343181,"uid":57018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:24:48.000Z","msg":"廢話唔多講，最想拋豬引玉，而家同大家盤點一下整蠱界最好玩又實用既寶物！用作開party就最岩！<br />\n<br />\n利申：所有寶物係要自行課金，好似玩模擬市民既package咁，自己揀。<br />\n<br />\n1. 臭： 惡臭噴霧 （臭彈）<br />\n臭彈唔share啦，呢枝野最好係唔會噴到自己個面，有個噴嘴，只會對住前面方向發出惡臭，「趕」走佢地，室內最岩玩，因為唔通風而且冇咁易反聞。<br />\n<br />\n［img]<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/2FQBwQW.png[/img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2FQBwQW.png%5B%2Fimg%5D&d=0ZQOgT4XWRiGBLzCIZSXcgu0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=1fcea5e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/2FQBwQW.png[/img]</a><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MdbkYvW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMdbkYvW.png&h=3eed854d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dLEuRQX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdLEuRQX.png&h=e3db41c6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f9WUivZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff9WUivZ.png&h=f7772790&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 辣：辣辣劑<br />\n唔多介紹，「防」身用，請人食譚仔大辣。<br />\n［img]<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/ErWkYxA.png[/img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FErWkYxA.png%5B%2Fimg%5D&d=0ZQOgT4XWRiGBLzCIZSXcgu0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=c7693e20\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/ErWkYxA.png[/img]</a><br />\n<br />\n3. 矇：彩粉噴樽（彩粉）<br />\n事先講明，安全地使用，用來做活動用，易清洗既，咁有咩作用？就係噴/掟矇醉酒鬧事，圍住靚女既狗公，如果帶眼罩會痴係眼罩到。情況危急可以一野噴落塊面到，放心佢洗就冇事，你趁個十秒要盡快「救」返個靚女。最勁係有得買按鈕式同補粉，買唔夠可以混埋其他粉，例如生粉頂頂。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SBFBwUO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSBFBwUO.png&h=230f8ec7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H5WMT79.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH5WMT79.png&h=75872f29&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/09EVNta.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F09EVNta.png&h=0aafcddd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 痕：癢癢粉<br />\n整蠱之首，「反」擊你討厭既人，已經進化到要沖涼先解到，用些少同類道具就可以擴散到前方既人，唔使縮埋放落人地件衫！絕對係現代版「生死符」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TpDGH4e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTpDGH4e.png&h=06dd7c72&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Kod7DCA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKod7DCA.png&h=b05d2c32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果開party，不妨考慮下入手，重覆：最緊要安全，正常都安全既。"},{"pid":"88a132d6a6728c04bc9980f6db63e17ec9c08005","tid":1343181,"uid":57018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3b495b30afad5155eba5d3fa025bd4d02f7f8527","tid":1343181,"uid":57018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:24:48.000Z","msg":"廢話唔多講，最想拋豬引玉，而家同大家盤點一下整蠱界最好玩又實用既寶物！用作開party就最岩！<br />\n<br />\n利申：所有寶物係要自行課金，好似玩模擬市民既package咁，自己揀。<br />\n<br />\n1. 臭： 惡臭噴霧 （臭彈）<br />\n臭彈唔share啦，呢枝野最好係唔會噴到自己個面，有個噴嘴，只會對住前面方向發出惡臭，「趕」走佢地，室內最岩玩，因為唔通風而且冇咁易反聞。<br />\n<br />\n［img]<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/2FQBwQW.png[/img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2FQBwQW.png%5B%2Fimg%5D&d=0ZQOgT4XWRiGBLzCIZSXcgu0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=1fcea5e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/2FQBwQW.png[/img]</a><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MdbkYvW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMdbkYvW.png&h=3eed854d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dLEuRQX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdLEuRQX.png&h=e3db41c6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f9WUivZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff9WUivZ.